# Changelog

## 2026-05-17 — Stage 1 backend deployed

Today I deployed the first working backend for Vantage to the DigitalOcean droplet.

### Completed
- Uploaded `vantage_check.sh` and `install_vantage.sh` to the server
- Installed the check script into `/usr/local/bin/`
- Created `/var/lib/vantage/`
- Created `/var/log/vantage.log`
- Added a cron job to run the check script every 5 minutes
- Generated `/var/www/html/status.json`
- Updated the live `index.html` page so it reads real output from `status.json`

### Result
Vantage is now working as a real cloud-hosted monitoring and server-status project rather than just a proposal page.
